{"tid":803433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贏國又贏！港台海洋污染簡體字樽佔66%","createTime":"2018-09-02T09:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T10:13:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6703d82f611d242dae2e324defe804a38d5dabfc","tid":803433,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180902/large/1535857349_841c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180902%2Flarge%2F1535857349_841c.jpg&h=71a6061d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球每年都有800萬公噸塑膠垃圾，膠樽更是十大海洋垃圾之一。香港環保團體綠惜地球與台灣環團在港台兩地進行共16場清潔運動，共收集超過5,200個廢棄膠樽。在能識別品牌的4,000多個瓶子中，簡體字品牌佔達66%。環保團體呼籲中國作為全球大海洋塑料垃圾製造國，有責任減塑，同時要求飲料供應商訂定減塑目標，對應海洋廢塑料危機。<br />\n<br />\n綠惜地球於今年8月在港島垃圾灣、大嶼山水口、南丫島、西貢、沙頭角、大埔三門仔、東涌河等，進行10次調查，共收集1,776個膠樽，當中有967個為繁體字膠樽，佔55%，簡體字膠樽則有678個，佔38%。至於台灣環團則在澎湖和新北進行共6次調查，收集2,665個膠樽，簡體字膠樽反多達2,260個，佔85%，繁體字有288個，佔11%。在眾多簡體字廢棄膠樽品牌中，以康師傅（33%）佔最多；娃哈哈（16%）和農夫山泉（14%）就分列二、三位。<br />\n<br />\n綠惜地球總幹事劉祉鋒則表示，環保署2015年發布有關調查，指95%垃圾為香港製造，內地只佔5%，綠惜地球認為比例值得商榷，促請環保署檢視調查方法，並與內地加強合作，堵截廢膠污染海洋。他又指，生產商應從源頭從消費者手上回收。而南韓實行生產者責任制，回收量高達八至九成，反之香港回收率僅9%是「醜死怪」。他促請香港政府盡快推行生產者責任制，增加市民和生產商回收誘因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180902/58635380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180902%2F58635380&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7f31e633\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180902%2F58635380&h=dc41c0fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180902/58635380</a>"},{"pid":"51e54624d7c6d847a1021dca220623d38c7ed391","tid":803433,"uid":38177,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"環保撚快滅贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee972f9ecb04f25f783a9c66df529c1d697a4db5","tid":803433,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁要禁飲管"},{"pid":"4ab73614993c38748b7acf3bbfff5bc46ddfa2b7","tid":803433,"uid":150609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:31:32.000Z","msg":"試下要係D飲管印繁體中文<br />\n<br />\n睇下係咪香港掉落海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b5b52949074af609549f691d7d37f109cccbe6","tid":803433,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"10幾億蝗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5169f36bbba5ff2039be513c4895e1ad56af6e9b","tid":803433,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾生產國"},{"pid":"62ab93413c3fab4a9d59c81e6105c6cd453613e0","tid":803433,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:45:20.000Z","msg":"環保撚出黎講兩句"},{"pid":"5ca1fea3b38ce75d47be9a61e30d9a9be2403658","tid":803433,"uid":194012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 環保署2015年發布有關調查，指95%垃圾為香港製造，內地只佔5%，綠惜地球認為比例值得商榷</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85fcb233640dcd1d567cf3d893316914de322b1","tid":803433,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ca1fea3b38ce75d47be9a61e30d9a9be2403658","tid":803433,"uid":194012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 環保署2015年發布有關調查，指95%垃圾為香港製造，內地只佔5%，綠惜地球認為比例值得商榷</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:13:23.000Z","msg":"咩嘢13億人1蚊都賺